; Coverage test for report.cc line 1214: -X (exchange) short option
; Tests currency conversion with -X option

P 2024/01/15 EUR $1.10

2024/01/15 Foreign Purchase
    Expenses:Travel    100 EUR
    Assets:Cash

test -X '$' reg
